Here is a CSS stylesheet that increases the font size to 20px, applies an italicized font style, and adds 70% transparency to all elements on the page:

```css
body {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-style: italic;
}

* {
    opacity: 0.7;
}
```

This stylesheet targets the `body` element and applies a `font-size` of 20px and a `font-style` of `italic` to all text on the page. It also uses the universal selector `*` to target all elements on the page and applies a 70% transparency using the `opacity` property set to 0.7.
